{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/CHASE.png?t=1737098710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 weeks ago, the Inquisition court sentenced Alice Kyteler to be burned at the stake, on suspicion of witchcraft and participation in the coven, but she managed to escape, on the way to the place of execution<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/3.png?t=1737098710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She hid in the forests of Blackwood and is probably still hiding there, until now <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/5.png?t=1737098710\" />As news arrives that residents of nearby villages are noticing strange phenomena in the forest and cases of missing childrenAnd livestock have become more frequent,<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/2.png?t=1737098710\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will have to take on the role of a mercenary of the Inquisition, go to the dark forest of Blackwood and fulfill the terms of the contract to find Alice Kyteler and enforce the sentence.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/6.png?t=1737098710\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have to explore this gloomy and dark world, collect information, study various magical rituals, find new chemicals, and decipher the riddles and exterminate the wickedness that inhabited the Blackwood Forest in various ways.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/1.png?t=1737098710\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/4.png?t=1737098710\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\